The paper discusses the use of data science, machine learning, and big data in cyber-security solutions, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the use of analytic models and methodologies for effective cyber-security projects, which could be classified under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also emphasizes the importance of methodology and resources for successful data science projects, which could be categorized under software engineering (cs.SE) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
